defs.name: Error
defs.value:
pub enum Error {

    #[error("Unknown codec")]
    UnknownCodec,

    #[error("Input too short")]
    InputTooShort,

    #[error("Failed to parse multihash")]
    ParsingError,

    #[error("Unrecognized CID version")]
    InvalidCidVersion,

    #[error(transparent)]
    Multihash(
              #[from]
              multihash::Error),

    #[error("Other cid Error: {0}")]
    Other(String),
}
defs.docs: Cid Error
